window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>***This is a dual narrated and multi-cast omnibus edition, including three stores from the Mystics and Mayhem world by Heather Renee. Each story can be listened to as a standalone, but they are best consumed consecutively.***</p> <p>Within this book you'll find three standalone books: <i>Christmas Mates</i>, <i>Fractured Mates</i>, and <i>Shattered Mates</i>. They are the final stories written within the Mystics and Mayhem universe and the perfect ending to this intriguing world.<br> <br> You'll meet new friends, connect with old favorites, and possibly even shed some tearsâ€”both of the sad and happy varieties.<br> <br> Now get ready. There's a holiday gathering with all the shenanigans to attend, vengeance to be had, risks to be taken, mates to claim, and families to find within this audiobook.<br> <br> Happy listening!</p>"; 
